## Test Class Naming Conventions

| Scenario | Pattern | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Standard unit test for a type | `<SUT>Test` | `AttachmentHandlerTest` |
| Large SUT split by feature | `Base<SUT>Test` + `<SUT><Feature>Test` | `BaseMessagingClientTest`, `MCAuthTest` |
| DTO/serialization suite (consolidated) | `RequestSerializationTest` | `RequestSerializationTest` |
| DTO/serialization split by type | `<Type>SerializationTest` | `EchoRequestSerializationTest` |

